public class RemoveAllMarkersFromProfile
extends RemoveAllMarkersFromItem

This implementation of a marker droplet will remove all marker items from a profile repository item.

The item used in the marker operation will automatically default to the current session profile when one isn't provided as an input parameter.

See Also:
RemoveAllMarkersFromItem
